    "name": "Chop Chop Together",
    "steam_appid": 3065360,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3065360/extras/1ae5ce96b05e1146a6580ebf43abf502.avif?t=1771859760\" width=600 height=150 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>组队行动。搞砸一切。完成工作。</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Chop Chop: Together</strong> 是一款支持 1–4 人游玩的混乱合作派对游戏。在这里，团队合作、混沌场面和一点点“背叛”并肩同行。扮演不同职业，与时间赛跑，并尽量（真的要很努力）别把友情搞崩。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >从渔船到繁忙的仓库，每一份工作乍看都很简单……<br> 直到一切开始失控。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3065360/extras/c71ac83bfa62dec743837765f02eec6b.poster.avif?t=1771859760\" width=1170 height=380 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3065360/extras/c71ac83bfa62dec743837765f02eec6b.webm?t=1771859760\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3065360/extras/c71ac83bfa62dec743837765f02eec6b.mp4?t=1771859760\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3065360/extras/237892d0e9fef25dcbc3d917a50ab499.avif?t=1771859760\" width=600 height=150 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🧑‍🤝‍🧑 <strong>一起玩（或互相对抗）</strong> 可单人游玩，或最多 4 人在线合作。<br> 协调配合、互相喊叫、陷入慌乱、随机应变！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🏅 <strong>本月员工模式</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >想来点竞争吗？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >解锁 <strong>本月员工</strong> 模式——在这个特殊模式中：</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >玩家彼此竞争<br>只有一人能获得特殊奖励<br>友情……暂时可有可无<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3065360/extras/df2e2639780c304055449a80b17caa28.poster.avif?t=1771859760\" width=1170 height=380 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3065360/extras/df2e2639780c304055449a80b17caa28.webm?t=1771859760\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3065360/extras/df2e2639780c304055449a80b17caa28.mp4?t=1771859760\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3065360/extras/c647eebc69822d27f88e1957df60e739.avif?t=1771859760\" width=600 height=150 /></span><br><br>📰 <strong>多种职业，无尽混乱</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >选择一个职业，直接跳进关卡：</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🎣 <strong>捕鱼</strong> – 钓鱼、煮章鱼、晾干螃蟹、切割、加工并交付订单</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >📦 <strong>仓库</strong> – 打包、分拣、发货……并祈祷正确的箱子能送到正确的地方</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >❓ <strong>惊喜工作</strong> –<br> 你可能会一边躲避巨龙火焰，一边作为中世纪铁匠锻造宝剑；<br> 也可能在零重力厨房里，烹饪在太空中漂浮的烤肉串！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3065360/extras/10ccd4b8d95044c5d0e18b23607ba8be.poster.avif?t=1771859760\" width=1170 height=380 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3065360/extras/10ccd4b8d95044c5d0e18b23607ba8be.webm?t=1771859760\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3065360/extras/10ccd4b8d95044c5d0e18b23607ba8be.mp4?t=1771859760\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3065360/extras/fbd0eab7f78fa30c13088f4e37167554.avif?t=1771859760\" width=600 height=150 /></span><br><br>🏠 <strong>你的大厅，你的规则</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >任务之间，在共享大厅中放松一下。<br> 花掉你赚到的金币。<br> 解锁外观道具。<br> 自由定制你的角色和大厅。<strong>。</strong><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3065360/extras/7f76089bf3b2044121256585760e9811.poster.avif?t=1771859760\" width=1170 height=380 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3065360/extras/7f76089bf3b2044121256585760e9811.webm?t=1771859760\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3065360/extras/7f76089bf3b2044121256585760e9811.mp4?t=1771859760\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3065360/extras/16b84ebed679f5c96def25bf5ed0a7a0.avif?t=1771859760\" width=600 height=150 /></span><br><br>非常适合派对、直播，<br> 以及“再来一局就好”的夜晚。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >一起合作。激烈竞争。<br><strong>欢迎来到 Chop Chop: Together。</strong><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3065360/extras/1148e2955073fc9d152a2cd9eedfca9d.poster.avif?t=1771859760\" width=1170 height=380 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3065360/extras/1148e2955073fc9d152a2cd9eedfca9d.webm?t=1771859760\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3065360/extras/1148e2955073fc9d152a2cd9eedfca9d.mp4?t=1771859760\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
